Name: Mini Putt
About the game: Mini Putt is a multiplayer minigolf game for you and your friends! Enjoy our carefully crafted maps and maps made by our awesome community using our advanced map editor! No, we will not charge for new maps, outfits, hats or anything! Features 16 Player Multiplayer Invite up to 16 of your friends into a game of Mini Putt to show of your skills. Ball Customisations Unlock balls, faces, hats and trails to stand out from the other putters. Advanced Map Editor Create your own awesome maps and share them with other putters. Terrain Editor 100s of unique models Awesome model components Free DLC We will not charge for any additional content that we add to Mini Putt, we want the game to be as fun as possible for everyone!
